Package: microclimAg
Title: Microclimate Analysis in Agricultural Landscapes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Riham", "DAHNOUN", 
           email = "riham.dahnoun@iav.ac.ma", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package for analyzing microclimatic variations in agricultural 
    landscapes using remote sensing data (MODIS LST, Landsat thermal), 
    vegetation indices (NDVI), weather station data, and land cover information.
    Includes tools for heat island detection, spatial interpolation, 
    clustering, and automated reporting.
